  "text": "Fundamentals of laparoscopic surgery is an educational program developed by SAGES. This program was launched in 2004 [CITATION_1] . The overall goal of the FLS program is to teach and assess the basic cognitive and psychomotor skills required to competently perform laparoscopic surgery [CITATION_2] .",
